<Default><b>[SERIE] For if anyone cuts
your long life short,</b></Default>

c0000001
00:00:05.170 --> 00:00:07.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it will be
the Demon King himself.</b></Default>

c0000002
00:00:09.760 --> 00:00:11.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Or it will be a human mage.</b></Default>

c0000003
00:01:44.230 --> 00:01:47.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[thunder rumbling]</b></Default>

c0000004
00:01:49.900 --> 00:01:56.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000005
00:02:11.720 --> 00:02:12.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[shatters]</b></Default>

c0000006
00:02:13.260 --> 00:02:16.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000007
00:02:16.390 --> 00:02:19.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[wind whooshing]</b></Default>

c0000008
00:02:19.640 --> 00:02:26.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000009
00:02:26.940 --> 00:02:28.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[thudding]</b></Default>

c0000010
00:02:30.110 --> 00:02:31.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crackling]</b></Default>

c0000011
00:02:33.490 --> 00:02:34.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[shatters]</b></Default>

c0000012
00:02:35.410 --> 00:02:38.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crackling]</b></Default>

c0000013
00:02:38.910 --> 00:02:45.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000014
00:02:49.210 --> 00:02:51.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[shattering]</b></Default>

c0000015
00:02:55.550 --> 00:02:56.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It blocked the spell.</b></Default>

c0000016
00:02:57.260 --> 00:03:00.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000017
00:03:00.720 --> 00:03:02.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Things are unfolding
as expected.</b></Default>

c0000018
00:03:04.100 --> 00:03:05.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>From here on out,</b></Default>

c0000019
00:03:06.060 --> 00:03:07.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it's a battle of attrition.</b></Default>

c0000020
00:03:14.950 --> 00:03:16.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RICHTER]
Methode was correct.</b></Default>

c0000021
00:03:16.780 --> 00:03:18.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They're right where
she said they would be.</b></Default>

c0000022
00:03:20.280 --> 00:03:21.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Try not to hold me back.</b></Default>

c0000023
00:03:22.750 --> 00:03:24.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Same goes for you, old man.</b></Default>

c0000024
00:03:24.700 --> 00:03:27.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000025
00:03:27.880 --> 00:03:30.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN] Methode has determined
the exact locations</b></Default>

c0000026
00:03:30.590 --> 00:03:31.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of the enemy combatants.</b></Default>

c0000027
00:03:32.340 --> 00:03:35.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If we're forced into a melee,
we'll certainly lose.</b></Default>

c0000028
00:03:35.800 --> 00:03:38.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So our strategy is the classic
divide and conquer!</b></Default>

c0000029
00:03:38.680 --> 00:03:40.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We stop them
before they can gather here.</b></Default>

c0000030
00:03:41.930 --> 00:03:44.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We've gone over
our weakest matchups.</b></Default>

c0000031
00:03:44.220 --> 00:03:46.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The person you'd
least like to face in battle</b></Default>

c0000032
00:03:46.560 --> 00:03:49.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>will be the one best equipped
to defeat your replica.</b></Default>

c0000033
00:03:50.980 --> 00:03:53.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And remember, unlike the enemy,</b></Default>

c0000034
00:03:53.110 --> 00:03:55.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we can communicate
and work together.</b></Default>

c0000035
00:03:55.950 --> 00:03:59.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000036
00:04:00.070 --> 00:04:02.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN] As long as we choose
our opponents strategically,</b></Default>

c0000037
00:04:03.870 --> 00:04:05.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we'll have the upper hand</b></Default>

c0000038
00:04:05.080 --> 00:04:07.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>both individually
and as a group.</b></Default>

c0000039
00:04:09.170 --> 00:04:12.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[blasting]
-[rumbling]</b></Default>

c0000040
00:04:15.970 --> 00:04:18.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN] Some will be
too strong to face alone.</b></Default>

c0000041
00:04:19.050 --> 00:04:21.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We'll counter that strength
with numbers.</b></Default>

c0000042
00:04:23.850 --> 00:04:25.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[thudding]</b></Default>

c0000043
00:04:25.430 --> 00:04:28.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000044
00:04:28.310 --> 00:04:29.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[shatters]</b></Default>

c0000045
00:04:29.730 --> 00:04:36.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000046
00:04:37.490 --> 00:04:39.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LAUFEN] This is so easy
it's almost laughable.</b></Default>

c0000047
00:04:39.650 --> 00:04:46.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000048
00:04:47.540 --> 00:04:49.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LAWINE] At this rate,
we'll stop them all,</b></Default>

c0000049
00:04:49.290 --> 00:04:50.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>no problem.</b></Default>

c0000050
00:04:50.420 --> 00:04:57.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000051
00:04:58.670 --> 00:05:00.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Seems we have a solid plan.</b></Default>

c0000052
00:05:00.800 --> 00:05:01.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN]
Indeed.</b></Default>

c0000053
00:05:01.720 --> 00:05:03.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Though a little luck
wouldn't hurt.</b></Default>

c0000054
00:05:04.180 --> 00:05:07.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[METHODE]
Hmm. There is one concern.</b></Default>

c0000055
00:05:07.980 --> 00:05:10.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm detecting fewer replicas
than we have test-takers.</b></Default>

c0000056
00:05:11.020 --> 00:05:13.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Which means that some of them
are unaccounted for.</b></Default>

c0000057
00:05:13.860 --> 00:05:16.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Notably, I can't find
Ms. Sense's double,</b></Default>

c0000058
00:05:16.690 --> 00:05:19.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who I believe we can all agree
poses the greatest threat.</b></Default>

c0000059
00:05:20.610 --> 00:05:22.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, I'm not sensing
its mana, either.</b></Default>

c0000060
00:05:23.240 --> 00:05:26.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And we can't afford to be
caught unawares by such a foe.</b></Default>

c0000061
00:05:26.790 --> 00:05:28.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If she comes at us from behind,</b></Default>

c0000062
00:05:28.290 --> 00:05:30.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>then I won't be able
to protect Fern.</b></Default>

c0000063
00:05:30.870 --> 00:05:32.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In the worst case,
we both could die.</b></Default>

c0000064
00:05:33.420 --> 00:05:35.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[METHODE] I've been
similarly unable to locate</b></Default>

c0000065
00:05:35.540 --> 00:05:37.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ms. Fern
or Mr. Denken's replicas.</b></Default>

c0000066
00:05:38.340 --> 00:05:39.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We'll have to search for them</b></Default>

c0000067
00:05:39.420 --> 00:05:42.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>using more precise,
close-range detection.</b></Default>

c0000068
00:05:44.050 --> 00:05:46.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you hadn't decided
to come along,</b></Default>

c0000069
00:05:46.220 --> 00:05:48.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we would have a lot less
to worry about right now.</b></Default>

c0000070
00:05:49.810 --> 00:05:52.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>One aspiring to the title
of first-class mage</b></Default>

c0000071
00:05:52.690 --> 00:05:55.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>must be able to overcome
both adversity and unfairness.</b></Default>

c0000072
00:05:56.400 --> 00:05:58.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Though, frankly,
this doesn't qualify as either.</b></Default>

c0000073
00:05:59.320 --> 00:06:00.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

c0000074
00:06:00.860 --> 00:06:02.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SENSE]
All you need to do to pass</b></Default>

c0000075
00:06:02.490 --> 00:06:04.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is watch each other's backs.</b></Default>

c0000076
00:06:05.240 --> 00:06:08.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is a kind test,
and a peaceful one.</b></Default>

c0000077
00:06:08.830 --> 00:06:10.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[shatters]</b></Default>

c0000078
00:06:12.290 --> 00:06:13.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[thuds]</b></Default>

c0000079
00:06:13.790 --> 00:06:16.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[clattering]</b></Default>

c0000080
00:06:17.460 --> 00:06:18.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm glad we won.</b></Default>

c0000081
00:06:19.920 --> 00:06:21.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But I can't say I enjoyed that.</b></Default>

c0000082
00:06:23.050 --> 00:06:24.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000083
00:06:26.430 --> 00:06:27.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RICHTER]
An ambush.</b></Default>

c0000084
00:06:28.060 --> 00:06:29.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[rumbling]</b></Default>

c0000085
00:06:29.970 --> 00:06:30.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000086
00:06:31.810 --> 00:06:32.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groans]</b></Default>

c0000087
00:06:34.730 --> 00:06:36.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Of course, it's you.</b></Default>

c0000088
00:06:37.400 --> 00:06:39.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I didn't notice
my mana detection slipping.</b></Default>

c0000089
00:06:41.820 --> 00:06:43.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[groans]
-[RICHTER] Lawine,</b></Default>

c0000090
00:06:43.530 --> 00:06:44.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you should break
your bottle, too.</b></Default>

c0000091
00:06:46.240 --> 00:06:48.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're old enough to know
when it's time to quit.</b></Default>

c0000092
00:06:50.290 --> 00:06:52.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just three years
till the next test.</b></Default>

c0000093
00:06:53.750 --> 00:06:55.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]
Damn it.</b></Default>

c0000094
00:06:55.210 --> 00:06:59.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000095
00:07:01.800 --> 00:07:03.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN]
I didn't make it in time.</b></Default>

c0000096
00:07:04.630 --> 00:07:07.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My assistance may have
extended the ordeal,</b></Default>

c0000097
00:07:07.300 --> 00:07:09.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but I doubt it would've changed
the outcome.</b></Default>

c0000098
00:07:11.470 --> 00:07:12.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN]
Even with its back to me,</b></Default>

c0000099
00:07:12.890 --> 00:07:14.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't detect any openings.</b></Default>

c0000100
00:07:15.640 --> 00:07:17.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Whether I can defeat it or not,</b></Default>

c0000101
00:07:17.400 --> 00:07:19.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>my job is to slow them down.</b></Default>

c0000102
00:07:22.110 --> 00:07:25.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, well, if it isn't Denken,
the fancy-pants Imperial Mage.</b></Default>

c0000103
00:07:26.410 --> 00:07:28.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, what's the situation, boss?</b></Default>

c0000104
00:07:29.910 --> 00:07:32.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You shouldn't go storming
into this lightly.</b></Default>

c0000105
00:07:32.740 --> 00:07:34.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't think that you can win.</b></Default>

c0000106
00:07:34.790 --> 00:07:36.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN]
I tend to agree.</b></Default>

c0000107
00:07:37.460 --> 00:07:38.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, tell me, Denken.</b></Default>

c0000108
00:07:38.920 --> 00:07:40.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If we want to conquer
the labyrinth,</b></Default>

c0000109
00:07:40.630 --> 00:07:42.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is beating her a must?</b></Default>

c0000110
00:07:42.630 --> 00:07:44.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, first, Frieren
is currently--</b></Default>

c0000111
00:07:44.460 --> 00:07:45.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Spare me the details.</b></Default>

c0000112
00:07:46.050 --> 00:07:47.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is this necessary or not?</b></Default>

c0000113
00:07:50.350 --> 00:07:51.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It is.</b></Default>

c0000114
00:07:53.220 --> 00:07:55.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then let me take care of her.</b></Default>

c0000115
00:07:55.390 --> 00:07:57.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How delusional are you?</b></Default>

c0000116
00:07:57.230 --> 00:07:59.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Denken is the strongest one
amongst us by far.</b></Default>

c0000117
00:08:00.190 --> 00:08:03.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And let's not forget that you
couldn't even best Wirbel.</b></Default>

c0000118
00:08:03.650 --> 00:08:04.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

c0000119
00:08:04.820 --> 00:08:07.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But that's not how
this works, now, is it?</b></Default>

c0000120
00:08:07.650 --> 00:08:09.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes, I'm a third-class mage,</b></Default>

c0000121
00:08:09.240 --> 00:08:11.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and yes, I am lacking
in experience.</b></Default>

c0000122
00:08:12.080 --> 00:08:14.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Both Denken and Wirbel
could beat me to a pulp.</b></Default>

c0000123
00:08:15.450 --> 00:08:18.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But I'm confident
that I can take down Sense.</b></Default>

c0000124
00:08:18.580 --> 00:08:19.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LAND]
Hm.</b></Default>

c0000125
00:08:19.500 --> 00:08:22.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My specialty
is well suited for this.</b></Default>

c0000126
00:08:22.840 --> 00:08:25.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's a spell that cuts
through almost anything.</b></Default>

c0000127
00:08:25.630 --> 00:08:26.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Reelseiden.</b></Default>

c0000128
00:08:27.300 --> 00:08:28.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I think I can cut something,</b></Default>

c0000129
00:08:28.930 --> 00:08:31.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can slice
and dice it all day.</b></Default>

c0000130
00:08:31.140 --> 00:08:33.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I don't think I can,
it's impenetrable.</b></Default>

c0000131
00:08:33.760 --> 00:08:35.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't know why you're
so sure of yourself.</b></Default>

c0000132
00:08:36.430 --> 00:08:39.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Defensive magic can block
that spell with great ease.</b></Default>

c0000133
00:08:39.480 --> 00:08:41.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[UBEL]
I almost forgot, four-eyes.</b></Default>

c0000134
00:08:41.650 --> 00:08:44.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You saw my little
sparring match with Wirbel.</b></Default>

c0000135
00:08:44.770 --> 00:08:45.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're right.</b></Default>

c0000136
00:08:45.860 --> 00:08:47.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The entire purpose
of defensive magic</b></Default>

c0000137
00:08:47.990 --> 00:08:49.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is to block attacks.</b></Default>

c0000138
00:08:49.650 --> 00:08:52.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's hard for me to imagine
cutting through that.</b></Default>

c0000139
00:08:52.780 --> 00:08:53.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I see.</b></Default>

c0000140
00:08:54.160 --> 00:08:55.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In that case,
your trick won't do</b></Default>

c0000141
00:08:55.580 --> 00:08:56.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>any good against Sense.</b></Default>

c0000142
00:08:57.830 --> 00:08:59.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just look at it.</b></Default>

c0000143
00:08:59.170 --> 00:09:01.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That hair is imbued with
so many layers of magic</b></Default>

c0000144
00:09:01.500 --> 00:09:04.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it makes utter child's play
of Wirbel's defensive spell.</b></Default>

c0000145
00:09:05.130 --> 00:09:07.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You should accept that
sort of logic doesn't matter.</b></Default>

c0000146
00:09:08.130 --> 00:09:10.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is a game
of pure visualization.</b></Default>

c0000147
00:09:11.550 --> 00:09:12.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, hold on.</b></Default>

c0000148
00:09:15.640 --> 00:09:16.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[UBEL]
Huh.</b></Default>

c0000149
00:09:17.430 --> 00:09:20.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I had a feeling that
Sorganeil wouldn't work on her.</b></Default>

c0000150
00:09:21.350 --> 00:09:24.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, I guess a person's hair
is a part of their body.</b></Default>

c0000151
00:09:24.860 --> 00:09:27.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's impossible to see
all of her at once.</b></Default>

c0000152
00:09:28.940 --> 00:09:31.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[smacks lips]
Reelseiden.</b></Default>

c0000153
00:09:33.030 --> 00:09:34.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SENSE]
Just as expected,</b></Default>

c0000154
00:09:34.370 --> 00:09:36.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ubel is the one
facing my replica.</b></Default>

c0000155
00:09:37.540 --> 00:09:39.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I already know who will win,</b></Default>

c0000156
00:09:39.460 --> 00:09:42.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and it will a be far cry
from a real fight.</b></Default>

c0000157
00:09:43.170 --> 00:09:44.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It happened two years ago,</b></Default>

c0000158
00:09:45.040 --> 00:09:47.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>during the second-class
mage exam.</b></Default>

c0000159
00:09:47.380 --> 00:09:49.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She made it past
the primary round</b></Default>

c0000160
00:09:49.380 --> 00:09:51.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and was attending
the second test</b></Default>

c0000161
00:09:51.090 --> 00:09:53.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>proctored by
the first-class mage Burg.</b></Default>

c0000162
00:09:54.050 --> 00:09:56.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He was so skilled
in defensive magic</b></Default>

c0000163
00:09:56.510 --> 00:09:58.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that he hadn't
been injured once</b></Default>

c0000164
00:09:58.140 --> 00:10:00.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>since passing his exam
and taking on the position.</b></Default>

c0000165
00:10:01.140 --> 00:10:03.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As such, the test
was structured around this.</b></Default>

c0000166
00:10:04.400 --> 00:10:06.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He wore his Immovable Cloak,</b></Default>

c0000167
00:10:06.610 --> 00:10:08.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a garment he created using mana</b></Default>

c0000168
00:10:08.980 --> 00:10:11.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that was woven
with so many defensive spells</b></Default>

c0000169
00:10:11.530 --> 00:10:13.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that no magical attack
could penetrate it.</b></Default>

c0000170
00:10:15.410 --> 00:10:16.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>For the second test,</b></Default>

c0000171
00:10:16.950 --> 00:10:19.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the examinees fired
offensive magic</b></Default>

c0000172
00:10:19.290 --> 00:10:20.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-against Burg and his cloak.
-[clanking]</b></Default>

c0000173
00:10:21.870 --> 00:10:22.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SENSE]
It was simple.</b></Default>

c0000174
00:10:22.960 --> 00:10:25.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If they could make him
take just one step back,</b></Default>

c0000175
00:10:25.670 --> 00:10:26.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>they passed.</b></Default>

c0000176
00:10:27.090 --> 00:10:29.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Killing would result
in disqualification,</b></Default>

c0000177
00:10:29.750 --> 00:10:31.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and there were limits imposed</b></Default>

c0000178
00:10:31.220 --> 00:10:33.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>on the offensive spells
they selected.</b></Default>

c0000179
00:10:33.630 --> 00:10:36.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That way, other mages wouldn't
be hurt by the onslaught.</b></Default>

c0000180
00:10:36.850 --> 00:10:37.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[BURG]
Next.</b></Default>

c0000181
00:10:42.310 --> 00:10:45.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SENSE] Not a single one of us
was worried about Burg.</b></Default>

c0000182
00:10:49.150 --> 00:10:50.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[slashing]</b></Default>

c0000183
00:10:53.110 --> 00:10:54.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[thudding]</b></Default>

c0000184
00:10:55.450 --> 00:10:57.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ooh. Cut too deep, huh?</b></Default>

c0000185
00:10:58.330 --> 00:11:01.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

c0000186
00:11:01.500 --> 00:11:03.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It was a complete
and utter shock</b></Default>

c0000187
00:11:03.250 --> 00:11:05.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>when he was easily killed
by a no-name girl.</b></Default>

c0000188
00:11:06.500 --> 00:11:08.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A very recent third-class mage.</b></Default>

c0000189
00:11:11.210 --> 00:11:13.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[UBEL] I feel like I passed
as much as I failed,</b></Default>

c0000190
00:11:13.380 --> 00:11:15.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but I guess that I get it.</b></Default>

c0000191
00:11:15.470 --> 00:11:16.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Can I please leave now?</b></Default>

c0000192
00:11:17.680 --> 00:11:19.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>After you answer one question.</b></Default>

c0000193
00:11:20.260 --> 00:11:21.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Go ahead.</b></Default>

c0000194
00:11:22.020 --> 00:11:24.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SENSE] How did you defeat
his Immovable Cloak?</b></Default>

c0000195
00:11:25.480 --> 00:11:26.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm.</b></Default>

c0000196
00:11:27.480 --> 00:11:28.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's see, now.</b></Default>

c0000197
00:11:29.270 --> 00:11:31.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Have you ever had to sew
anything before, Sense?</b></Default>

c0000198
00:11:32.230 --> 00:11:34.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I haven't. Is that pertinent?</b></Default>

c0000199
00:11:34.820 --> 00:11:37.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[UBEL] You do seem like
you come from a rich family.</b></Default>

c0000200
00:11:38.070 --> 00:11:39.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Or maybe you can magic away</b></Default>

c0000201
00:11:39.620 --> 00:11:41.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>all those
normal-person problems.</b></Default>

c0000202
00:11:42.740 --> 00:11:43.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>To be honest,</b></Default>

c0000203
00:11:44.750 --> 00:11:47.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've never actually
tried it myself</b></Default>

c0000204
00:11:47.170 --> 00:11:49.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>because I'm way too clumsy.</b></Default>

c0000205
00:11:49.500 --> 00:11:50.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[snips]</b></Default>

c0000206
00:11:52.300 --> 00:11:53.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But I used to watch
my big sister</b></Default>

c0000207
00:11:54.050 --> 00:11:56.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-do it all the time.
-[rips]</b></Default>

c0000208
00:11:59.930 --> 00:12:02.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[UBEL] After you find
a pretty piece of cloth,</b></Default>

c0000209
00:12:02.930 --> 00:12:05.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you place the scissors
against it like this</b></Default>

c0000210
00:12:05.180 --> 00:12:07.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and slide them right through.</b></Default>

c0000211
00:12:08.270 --> 00:12:10.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The sound it makes
is so satisfying.</b></Default>

c0000212
00:12:14.940 --> 00:12:17.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's always brought
some strange joy.</b></Default>

c0000213
00:12:18.280 --> 00:12:19.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Where are you going with this?</b></Default>

c0000214
00:12:20.660 --> 00:12:22.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's all visualization.</b></Default>

c0000215
00:12:22.740 --> 00:12:24.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I know cloth can be cut.</b></Default>

c0000216
00:12:24.500 --> 00:12:25.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I imagined cutting it,</b></Default>

c0000217
00:12:26.540 --> 00:12:28.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>then used my magic
to snip away.</b></Default>

c0000218
00:12:30.670 --> 00:12:32.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SENSE]
This woman is insane.</b></Default>

c0000219
00:12:33.380 --> 00:12:36.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's true anyone can
imagine cutting cloth.</b></Default>

c0000220
00:12:36.420 --> 00:12:38.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The dullest of the dull
could muster that much.</b></Default>

c0000221
00:12:39.840 --> 00:12:41.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But the world of magic</b></Default>

c0000222
00:12:41.180 --> 00:12:43.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>isn't as simple
as she makes it seem.</b></Default>

c0000223
00:12:44.100 --> 00:12:45.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A spell can't create anything</b></Default>

c0000224
00:12:45.810 --> 00:12:48.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the caster can't
perfectly visualize.</b></Default>

c0000225
00:12:49.810 --> 00:12:51.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just as an ant can't imagine</b></Default>

c0000226
00:12:51.810 --> 00:12:54.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>crushing a colossal dragon
underfoot.</b></Default>

c0000227
00:12:55.480 --> 00:12:58.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Precious few mages
can imagine penetrating a cloak</b></Default>

c0000228
00:12:58.820 --> 00:13:00.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that is known
to be impregnable.</b></Default>

c0000229
00:13:00.860 --> 00:13:03.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>To do so goes
against all reason.</b></Default>

c0000230
00:13:03.870 --> 00:13:06.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>One glance at the thing,
and you can tell it blocks</b></Default>

c0000231
00:13:06.370 --> 00:13:08.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>even the strongest
magical attacks.</b></Default>

c0000232
00:13:08.790 --> 00:13:11.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It doesn't take a first-class
mage to see that.</b></Default>

c0000233
00:13:11.920 --> 00:13:13.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>An idiot could pick up
on its power.</b></Default>

c0000234
00:13:15.710 --> 00:13:18.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As long as people remain
intelligent organisms,</b></Default>

c0000235
00:13:19.300 --> 00:13:21.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we cannot escape
those logical fetters.</b></Default>

c0000236
00:13:22.800 --> 00:13:26.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But she relied on intuition
over intelligence.</b></Default>

c0000237
00:13:27.140 --> 00:13:29.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Despite intellectually
understanding</b></Default>

c0000238
00:13:29.390 --> 00:13:30.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that it couldn't be cut,</b></Default>

c0000239
00:13:31.100 --> 00:13:34.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she constructed a vision
of slicing through the cloak</b></Default>

c0000240
00:13:34.480 --> 00:13:36.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>guided by feeling alone.</b></Default>

c0000241
00:13:37.110 --> 00:13:38.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>From what I've seen,</b></Default>

c0000242
00:13:38.280 --> 00:13:41.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>her mind hardly functions
like a person's at all.</b></Default>

c0000243
00:13:41.740 --> 00:13:44.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is in the realm of genius.</b></Default>

c0000244
00:13:45.700 --> 00:13:47.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Can I hit the road, or what?</b></Default>

c0000245
00:13:47.830 --> 00:13:48.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes.</b></Default>

c0000246
00:13:50.960 --> 00:13:52.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>By the way, Sense.</b></Default>

c0000247
00:13:52.580 --> 00:13:54.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Real pretty hair you've got.</b></Default>

c0000248
00:13:54.750 --> 00:13:56.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It must be a nightmare
to maintain.</b></Default>

c0000249
00:13:59.920 --> 00:14:01.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SENSE]
I lost to her in that office</b></Default>

c0000250
00:14:01.840 --> 00:14:04.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>without the question of combat
on the horizon.</b></Default>

c0000251
00:14:05.010 --> 00:14:07.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I simply cannot imagine
beating Ubel.</b></Default>

c0000252
00:14:09.060 --> 00:14:11.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She is my worst match.</b></Default>

c0000253
00:14:13.600 --> 00:14:15.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[thudding]</b></Default>

c0000254
00:14:17.480 --> 00:14:20.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You all need to take a step
out of your heads.</b></Default>

c0000255
00:14:20.190 --> 00:14:21.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hair is something to be cut.</b></Default>

c0000256
00:14:24.490 --> 00:14:26.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SENSE]
Maintaining my hair?</b></Default>

c0000257
00:14:26.660 --> 00:14:28.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's hellish, indeed.</b></Default>

c0000258
00:14:28.830 --> 00:14:30.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A tangled disaster.</b></Default>

c0000259
00:14:31.660 --> 00:14:32.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000260
00:14:33.580 --> 00:14:35.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[UBEL]
Then perhaps you should cut it.</b></Default>

c0000261
00:14:38.550 --> 00:14:40.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[WIRBEL]
I think I've got the picture.</b></Default>

c0000262
00:14:41.050 --> 00:14:42.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're buying time.</b></Default>

c0000263
00:14:42.260 --> 00:14:44.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Fending off the copies
until Frieren defeats</b></Default>

c0000264
00:14:44.380 --> 00:14:46.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the Spiegel and puts an end
to the madness.</b></Default>

c0000265
00:14:46.470 --> 00:14:47.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes, that's right.</b></Default>

c0000266
00:14:48.640 --> 00:14:49.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then good news.</b></Default>

c0000267
00:14:49.930 --> 00:14:51.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We've defeated
three of them already.</b></Default>

c0000268
00:14:52.140 --> 00:14:54.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That certainly makes
things easier.</b></Default>

c0000269
00:14:54.730 --> 00:14:57.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In that case... Oh, my.</b></Default>

c0000270
00:14:57.400 --> 00:15:00.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I just picked up
on a substantial shift.</b></Default>

c0000271
00:15:00.190 --> 00:15:02.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ms. Sense's replica
has been destroyed.</b></Default>

c0000272
00:15:02.490 --> 00:15:04.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-This mana.
-[clinking]</b></Default>

c0000273
00:15:04.360 --> 00:15:06.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It would seem the
third-class mage</b></Default>

c0000274
00:15:06.360 --> 00:15:08.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ubel is responsible.</b></Default>

c0000275
00:15:08.160 --> 00:15:09.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's rather surprising.</b></Default>

c0000276
00:15:09.950 --> 00:15:11.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is it?</b></Default>

c0000277
00:15:11.200 --> 00:15:13.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ubel would be
a disaster for Sense.</b></Default>

c0000278
00:15:14.000 --> 00:15:16.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Battles between mages are
more like rock-paper-scissors</b></Default>

c0000279
00:15:16.960 --> 00:15:18.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>than competitions of strength.</b></Default>

c0000280
00:15:18.960 --> 00:15:20.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>However, it's a complex game</b></Default>

c0000281
00:15:20.840 --> 00:15:24.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>featuring many more weapons
than scissors, paper, and rock.</b></Default>

c0000282
00:15:24.510 --> 00:15:26.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[WIRBEL] And you want to throw
a few more weapons</b></Default>

c0000283
00:15:26.430 --> 00:15:28.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>into the mix
for your side, huh?</b></Default>

c0000284
00:15:29.050 --> 00:15:30.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Wirbel grunts]</b></Default>

c0000285
00:15:30.810 --> 00:15:33.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sure. We'll help you
slow down the replicas</b></Default>

c0000286
00:15:33.390 --> 00:15:34.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and hopefully take a few out.</b></Default>

c0000287
00:15:35.690 --> 00:15:37.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Blindly trusting others
isn't a habit of mine,</b></Default>

c0000288
00:15:37.900 --> 00:15:40.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but I'm also not dumb enough</b></Default>

c0000289
00:15:40.110 --> 00:15:42.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-to let victory
slip through my fingers. -Hmm.</b></Default>

c0000290
00:15:43.900 --> 00:15:46.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[METHODE] Currently, there
are two dangerous replicas</b></Default>

c0000291
00:15:46.570 --> 00:15:48.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we need to put all
of our energy into stopping.</b></Default>

c0000292
00:15:49.950 --> 00:15:51.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've determined
the location of one of them.</b></Default>

c0000293
00:15:52.080 --> 00:15:53.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mister Denken's replica</b></Default>

c0000294
00:15:53.330 --> 00:15:54.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is rapidly approaching
the bottom.</b></Default>

c0000295
00:15:55.290 --> 00:15:58.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I would like you to deal
with it as quickly as possible.</b></Default>

c0000296
00:15:58.170 --> 00:15:59.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm.</b></Default>

c0000297
00:15:59.670 --> 00:16:00.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I will take Fern's.</b></Default>

c0000298
00:16:00.880 --> 00:16:02.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And though fighting it
will be no easy task,</b></Default>

c0000299
00:16:02.920 --> 00:16:05.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I worry finding it
will prove harder.</b></Default>

c0000300
00:16:05.380 --> 00:16:08.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That girl is incredibly skilled
at concealing her mana</b></Default>

c0000301
00:16:08.090 --> 00:16:09.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for long periods.</b></Default>

c0000302
00:16:09.720 --> 00:16:11.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If we don't find
her double soon,</b></Default>

c0000303
00:16:11.890 --> 00:16:14.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it could ambush
and kill one of us.</b></Default>

c0000304
00:16:14.310 --> 00:16:16.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you really think
you can handle it on your own?</b></Default>

c0000305
00:16:17.190 --> 00:16:20.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Working alone will help me
focus on mana detection.</b></Default>

c0000306
00:16:20.190 --> 00:16:21.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[EHRE]
Don't underestimate it.</b></Default>

c0000307
00:16:21.770 --> 00:16:23.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Fern is strong.</b></Default>

c0000308
00:16:23.190 --> 00:16:25.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm a bit
of a jack of all trades,</b></Default>

c0000309
00:16:25.150 --> 00:16:27.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but restraining spells
are my forte.</b></Default>

c0000310
00:16:29.240 --> 00:16:31.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Besides, with her permission,
of course,</b></Default>

c0000311
00:16:31.200 --> 00:16:32.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I tested my binding magic...
Well?</b></Default>

c0000312
00:16:32.580 --> 00:16:34.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-...on the actual Miss Fern...
-I can't move at all.</b></Default>

c0000313
00:16:34.120 --> 00:16:35.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>...and had great success.</b></Default>

c0000314
00:16:36.370 --> 00:16:37.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[WIRBEL]
All right.</b></Default>

c0000315
00:16:37.830 --> 00:16:40.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>C'mon, let's go
fight this thing.</b></Default>

c0000316
00:16:42.250 --> 00:16:44.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LAND]
Ubel. What's going on?</b></Default>

c0000317
00:16:45.300 --> 00:16:47.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This isn't some trick
of the mind, is it?</b></Default>

c0000318
00:16:47.970 --> 00:16:49.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm gonna say no.</b></Default>

c0000319
00:16:49.930 --> 00:16:52.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Tricks of the mind usually
don't start with the body.</b></Default>

c0000320
00:16:53.810 --> 00:16:54.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

c0000321
00:16:55.350 --> 00:16:58.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[UBEL] Madame copy-cat
is back and ready to play.</b></Default>

c0000322
00:16:58.230 --> 00:17:04.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000323
00:17:05.150 --> 00:17:08.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Until the Spiegel is dead,
it looks like our replicas</b></Default>

c0000324
00:17:08.240 --> 00:17:10.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>will just keep
coming around for more.</b></Default>

c0000325
00:17:10.450 --> 00:17:13.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nothing stirs the soul quite
like a battle of attrition.</b></Default>

c0000326
