c0000336
00:18:05.580 --> 00:18:07.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
I suppose I have no choice.</b></Default>

c0000337
00:18:08.550 --> 00:18:10.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The vulnerability
in my mana detection</b></Default>

c0000338
00:18:10.720 --> 00:18:12.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>isn't large enough
