c0000348
00:18:34.950 --> 00:18:36.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
If I focus on defense,</b></Default>

c0000349
00:18:36.780 --> 00:18:38.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>nothing that slips past
will kill me.</b></Default>

c0000350
00:18:39.410 --> 00:18:42.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All right.
What strategy should we use?</b></Default>

c0000351
00:18:42.250 --> 00:18:45.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[explosions]</b></Default>

c0000352
00:18:46.290 --> 00:18:47.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
It's up to you.</b></Default>

c0000353
00:18:47.750 --> 00:18:49.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you think we can win,</b></Default>

c0000354
00:18:49.380 --> 00:18:50.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have no doubt we can.</b></Default>

c0000355
00:18:51.510 --> 00:18:53.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] How can you be
so sure about that?</b></Default>

c0000356
00:18:54.130 --> 00:18:55.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Because I know you, Fern,</b></Default>

c0000357
00:18:55.840 --> 00:18:58.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and I've underestimated you
the whole time.</b></Default>

c0000358
00:18:58.390 --> 00:18:59.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh.</b></Default>

c0000359
00:19:02.600 --> 00:19:04.390 line:90% align:center
