c0000369
00:20:03.750 --> 00:20:05.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but that wound is fatal.</b></Default>

c0000370
00:20:05.830 --> 00:20:07.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I should finish.</b></Default>

