00:20:09.750 --> 00:20:11.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[gasps]
-[explosion]</b></Default>

c0000372
00:20:12.000 --> 00:20:14.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[rumbling]</b></Default>

c0000373
00:20:15.460 --> 00:20:16.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
What just happened?</b></Default>

c0000374
00:20:17.010 --> 00:20:18.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did it attack me?</b></Default>

c0000375
00:20:19.010 --> 00:20:20.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm not sensing any mana.</b></Default>

c0000376
00:20:21.430 --> 00:20:22.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Whatever it did,</b></Default>

c0000377
00:20:22.890 --> 00:20:25.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't even recognize it
as a spell.</b></Default>

c0000378
00:20:27.730 --> 00:20:30.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Incredible, Mistress Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000379
00:20:30.770 --> 00:20:32.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So this is the height of magic.</b></Default>

c0000380
00:20:33.520 --> 00:20:34.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh.</b></Default>

c0000381
00:20:34.650 --> 00:20:37.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But my, how unlike you.</b></Default>

c0000382
00:20:39.870 --> 00:20:41.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're wide open.</b></Default>

c0000383
00:20:42.240 --> 00:20:49.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000384
00:20:51.540 --> 00:20:53.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Excellent work, Fern.</b></Default>

c0000385
00:20:55.170 --> 00:20:56.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'd say it's been
