c0000394
00:21:32.540 --> 00:21:33.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wirbel?</b></Default>

c0000395
00:21:33.790 --> 00:21:35.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Can you please carry me?</b></Default>

c0000396
00:21:35.630 --> 00:21:38.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You two just can't stay
on your feet, can you?</b></Default>

c0000397
00:21:48.100 --> 00:21:49.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We've lived to see the bottom</b></Default>

c0000398
00:21:49.560 --> 00:21:51.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of the Ruins
of the King's Tomb.</b></Default>

c0000399
00:21:53.100 --> 00:21:55.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Congratulations. You have
conquered the labyrinth.</b></Default>

c0000400
00:21:56.820 --> 00:21:59.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is a great achievement
fit for a first-class mage.</b></Default>

c0000401
00:22:00.030 --> 00:22:02.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You have proven yourselves
worthy in my eyes.</b></Default>

c0000402
00:22:03.780 --> 00:22:05.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As promised, everyone
who made it here</b></Default>

c0000403
00:22:06.030 --> 00:22:07.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>has passed the second test</b></Default>

c0000404
00:22:07.490 --> 00:22:09.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and will continue
