c0000414
00:22:29.390 --> 00:22:30.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
And so very scary.</b></Default>

c0000415
00:22:30.980 --> 00:22:32.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And with that,</b></Default>

