00:22:32.190 --> 00:22:34.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the second trial
has drawn to a close.</b></Default>

c0000417
00:22:36.360 --> 00:22:38.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[EDEL] They're
warriors, escape artists,</b></Default>

c0000418
00:22:38.400 --> 00:22:39.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and healers to boot.</b></Default>

c0000419
00:22:40.240 --> 00:22:42.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Neat, huh? Don't you think so?</b></Default>

